tags.description: Not allowed to enter officially, but this is more or less the only way to get to the ficus trees. Brbed wire with a hole at the bottom...

tags.inscription:
Founder of children's Tropical Forests U.K.
Her Love for this forest, its people, 
and its creatures
Inspired her to dedicate her life
to help establish in Costa Rica 
the first international children's rain forest,
Bosque Eterno De Los Ninos.
tags.name: Tina Jolliffe

tags.description: The Road Ends Here. Farm access only beyond this point. As of 2022-03-13 There is some construction and dirt being added to the road beyond this point.
